##Under the outbreak, 100 daily photos from around the country

Micro Signal Fengmianmedia

Function introduction, wind surface, photography new media. With the Wind Edu (photography humanities education) , for the wind surface Fengmian two brands.

The new coronary pneumonia (COVID-19) since the end of 2019 has changed the life track of almost every Chinese. Today, in addition to the medical workers and epidemic prevention workers who have to rush to the front line because of work, most people are trapped at home, waiting, anxiety, anger, helplessness and other emotions mixed every day and night. As advocates of photography to see and intervene in society, intervention in life, what can we do?

In "1,000 Chinese families taking selfies: The daily life of those who stay at home during the 2020 Spring Festival epidemic" and "don't go out! Come join the online film Review Exchange for Free" , i have seen many pictures of daily life under the epidemic, which were taken by film friends all over the country.

Warm tip: Even if the outbreak appears to improve, please also photography friends must pay attention to self-protection, safety first.

To ease the anxiety of "not being able to go out" , on January 30,2020, at the suggestion of "bicycle-sharing cemetery photographer" Wu Guoyong, with my new photography media, Fengmian, we launched the "1,000 Chinese family selfies: The daily life of those who stay at home during the 2020 Spring Festival" campaign, "As witnesses to this great event, we also hope to leave behind the daily lives of ordinary people who are carried by this great event, because each of us is a part of this history, and together with the Spring Festival in the year of Gengzi, will leave us indelible memories, " Wu said, the campaign received positive responses and contributions from film fans across the country; on February 4, tencent news set up a platform to participate in the campaign's promotion, and received 2.475 million readings and 16,000 submissions; on February 14, supchina (China News Service) , with "tens of thousands of households: a portrait of Chinese life during the coronavirus era" as the title, featured, published the campaign collection of graphics and text.

Wu Guoyong, Xiangyang, Hubei Province, old father-in-law's home, January 24,2020 New Year's Eve dinner

As of press time, the platform built by tencent had received 2.475 million views and 16,000 submissions.

Selfie collection (optional)

Special thanks to Qian Haifeng, Lu Tingchuan, Zhang Xiaowu, Liu Shutong, Li Lin, Dai Jianyong, Wang Xiangyang, Luo Jinqian and other well-known photographers and all the film contributors.

Qian Haifeng, Wuxi, February 7,2020

During the Spring Festival travel period, I took 10 trains to continue to film the Spring Festival travel projects, had passed the source of this epidemic in Hubei. Protocol dictates that I stay at home for two weeks. I had to walk back and forth in every car on every train, and when no one was wearing a mask, I didn't wear one, and I came into contact with a large number of passengers, becoming a virus-infected indeterminate. Not that I'm too worried about it, 10 years of backpacking, some experience, no panic, the only thing that bothers me is living with my parents, knowing that it's impossible to be completely disconnected from them, cOMFORT IN MIND: I will not be affected. I have been concerned about the train ride whether there is an updated confirmed case, check after no, such as take a pill to calm down. During the home quarantine, the community workers are very responsible, every day call to ask if the body is not feeling well, and video, said home what needs community can help solve. Every few days, the community will send someone to send me the daily food I need, on the door to tell, home quarantine these days, I cook at home every day, my mother also praised me. At the end of the quarantine period, home inspection, everything is normal, I stood at the door with the release of quarantine medical observation notice, ask the community staff to take a photo, said: Extraordinary Times, a souvenir. After getting the notice did not immediately go out, there is nothing particularly happy and excited, the heart is still very calm.

Related: Spring Festival travel in the midst of an epidemic: At first, no one wore a mask

Lu Tingchuan, Tianqiao District, Shandong Province, Lantern Festival on the 15th day of the first month

What time is it? My 85-year-old mother stays at home, getting up at 6 a.m. , making eight trips from the bedroom to the kitchen. That's what she asks most. She said that only time is real, now can do only wait, wait for the passage of time, wait for the spring.

Zhang Xiaowu, Hangzhou, Zhejiang Province, 2020 Spring Festival

He left home years ago this year and rushed to Hangzhou to spend the New Year with his beloved. At this time, I have obviously felt the arrival of the epidemic, but did not think of the severity to this extent, had to consciously isolate themselves in the rental house. A lover is a doctor who continues to do her job, and I am faced with a sea of information every day, trying to understand the truth of reality, but in this situation, I can not see the truth, and I can not see the truth, and the loss of individual life is so real, so sad. Life in a mobile phone is different. I dare not and will not easily believe it, but I have to believe it. The epidemic has pulled down our fig leaf piece by piece. It is not all good or all good. All moving should be moved, i believe in cause and effect in this world, and time will tell. All this time, photography seemed to be moving away from me, like wearing a ten-layer mask, making a sound so far away, the real us so weak, reflecting on the disaster, fearing life, I chose to respect. I took a picture of myself, in a weak light, and I was trying to see where the light was going, and maybe change would come from that.

Liu Shutong, Jinan, Shandong Province, selected from the "thermometer of my home" series during the epidemic period of new crown pneumonia

The days when we couldn't go out at home, apart from three meals a day, were the days when we took our family's temperature to make sure we were all healthy. I put these trivial daily into the "thermometer" series, to commemorate this special period.

Li Lin, Dongying, Shandong Province

February 9,2020, is the first day of primary and secondary school. The outbreak of school suspension, through the network of classes, the daughter of a high school first-year at home through the school's live learning. So far, there have been no confirmed cases of "new crown pneumonia" in my city, Dongying City, Shandong Province.

Dai Jianyong, Wuyuan County

Wuyuan County was shut down for 13 days, and every day we were trapped in our homes, wearing masks when he stood outside his house. He said he wanted to act like a virus and rush over, followed by his mother, Zhu Fengjuan.

Wang Xiangyang, Zhumadian, Henan Province, Wednesday, February 12,2020

It's a neighborhood in Zhumadian. Residents go out to purchase living materials, from the community temporary construction of disinfection channels into the community. This anti-epidemic disinfection tunnel is equipped with six humidifiers equipped with a special "disinfectant solution" , which kills the residents in and out of their bodies by spraying them continuously, residents go out to purchase living materials in and out of the community need to go through the disinfection channel disinfection for two minutes.

Luo Jinqian, Guangxi Autonomous Region, Liuzhou, January 31,2020 the seventh day of the Lunar New Year

The seventh day of the New Year is my in-laws'birthday. The Old Lady turned 85, and on this day every year, the sisters would come back to celebrate her birthday, often setting two tables. This year, because of the spread of COVID-19, people do not go out to pay New Year's greetings. We were afraid to go out and order a cake. Rummaging through the cupboard, I found a small box of birthday candles and stuck them on the Fortune Orange. I dressed up the old man and the old woman again and took this picture and sent it to the family group to make everyone happy.

Gong Hong, in front of her home in Ciudad del Este, Hainan Province, on January 25,2020

Mother-in-law, daughter-in-law, in-laws, myself (second from left) and Mr. The daughter is more than 4 months pregnant, husband and wife and in-laws came from Beijing for the Spring Festival, do not want to meet the epidemic. The epidemic has brought us a special Spring Festival.

Zhu Weibin, Yuan'an County, February 13,2020

My father, who is 85, and my mother, 79, had promised me a photo with my camera for the New Year, but the sudden outbreak of pneumonia threw the whole thing off. Dad's been talking about how we're not GONNA get a family portrait this year. I texted the family group, each taking a self portrait with a mask, and during the outbreak I cobbled together a family photo to satisfy my father's wishes. Hope the epidemic quickly over, all people are safe, is the greatest happiness.

Qi Yong. This year passed a special year, stay at home where can not go, online Weibo, mood ups and downs do not know what to say, took this film to express my mood at this time.
